Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.93,0:02:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以去車上待著...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We could jump in the car if...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這兒等著\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We'll wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.30,0:02:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你給議員買生日禮物了嗎  -沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Did you get the congressman anything for his birthday? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我買了袖釦  銀質的  有他的...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I got him cufflinks. Silver, with his --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.77,0:03:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不談論生日  不送禮物\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We don't talk about birthdays. We don't do gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.59,0:03:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.63,0:03:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去把袖釦退了吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You should return the cufflinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道格\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Doug?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.03,0:03:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在給你打電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tried calling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.57,0:03:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我把手機留在...  -我們得談談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- I left my phone in the... - We need to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.43,0:03:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯蒂娜  我剛剛跟她談過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Christina. I just spoke to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.90,0:03:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐伊...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did Zoe...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.78,0:03:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  但還不止\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah. But that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們還找到了瑞秋\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They tracked down Rachel, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.73,0:03:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭西斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Francis?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我說說瑞秋  她在哪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tell me about Rachel. Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.68,0:03:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我控制住她了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have her under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答非所問\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's not what I asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.76,0:03:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我送她回家了  不用擔心她\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I drove her home. We don't have to worry about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.46,0:03:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你當初也這麼說斯克斯基女士\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You said the same about Ms. Skorsky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.14,0:03:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有別人嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Anyone else involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.77,0:03:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有簡寧和佐伊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just Janine and Zoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們在查羅素酒駕的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They asked about Russo's arrest
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.27,0:03:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且知道他去找過科佩尼科\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and they know he went to see Kapeniak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.32,0:03:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想他們應該就知道這些了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I assume that's as far as they've gotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.36,0:03:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要想當然\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Assume nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去告訴巴尼·豪爾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll alert Barney Hull.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿佐伊怎麼辦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What do you want me to do about Zoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對付佐伊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll handle Zoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.56,0:03:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去辦事吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.26,0:03:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.46,0:04:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拿走了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I emptied it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.26,0:04:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你週二就又老一歲了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're another year older on Tuesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統可不能抽菸\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And we can't have a vice president who smokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.61,0:04:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能結束嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can you finish?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.86,0:04:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.54,0:04:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我完事了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  就是完事了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Nothing. I just said finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.80,0:04:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想...如果你不想...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I don't want just -- if you're not...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.79,0:04:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  隨便了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Okay, fine. Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐伊  是我做錯了什麼嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Zoe, did I do something that made you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.54,0:04:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐伊  你不能說一句完事了  然後就停下啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Zoe, you can't say something like "just finish" and then shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.17,0:05:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡很安全  佐伊  我不是他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is safe, Zoe. I'm not him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.03,0:05:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  傑姬\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Good morning, Jackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.10,0:05:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,理查德·拉塞爾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Richard Russell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.10,0:05:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}長期反對民權運動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.16,0:05:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1963年  《民權法案》\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Civil Rights Act. 1963.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是所有人都能留下美名\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not everyone can be on the right side of history.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.79,0:05:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連林登也曾站錯隊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, not even Lyndon for a time,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但沒有拉塞爾  林登也當不上多數黨領袖\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but he would have never become majority leader without him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是沒有約翰遜參議院大樓\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, there's no Johnson Senate building.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}有拉塞爾參議院大樓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.76,0:05:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  只能委屈他拿一棟總統圖書館湊合了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. He had to settle for a presidential library.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.39,0:05:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們都好久沒機會聊聊了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So it's been some time since you and I have had a chance to catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.09,0:05:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的工作做得很出色  傑姬\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You've been an outstanding deputy, Jackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.83,0:05:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比你那些老練的同事還高效\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Far more effective than your more seasoned colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.67,0:05:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能建立同盟  必要時還有股狠勁\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're a coalition builder, a fighter when you have to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.26,0:05:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我  你怎麼看自己的前途\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tell me, where do you see yourself headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想做眾議院軍事委員會主席\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'd like to aim for the chair of Armed Services.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.23,0:05:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者眾議院國土安全委員會主席\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Or Homeland Security.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.84,0:06:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你考慮過進入領導層嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Have you ever considered serving in the leadership?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.27,0:06:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想那至少也得等八...十年了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I figure that might be possible eight, ten years from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.20,0:06:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我說你這一屆就能進入領導層呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, what if I suggested that you could serve in leadership this term.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接替我  做黨鞭\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}To replace me. As whip.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要接任副總統了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're being tapped for VP.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是這樣吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's assume that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.86,0:06:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-這也說得通  但我做黨鞭  -是的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Well, that makes sense. But me as whip? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是個第三任女議員\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A third-term congresswoman?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.27,0:06:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的能力有目共睹  而且還參過戰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A universally admired incumbent who also happens to be a war veteran.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.13,0:06:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按順序也該是韋伯  或巴克沃特\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Webb is next in line. Or Buchwalter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.29,0:06:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以  你想想這意味著什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So just consider that for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.80,0:06:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們會牽制彼此的選票\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They'll draw votes from one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒說你會贏得很輕鬆\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, I'm not saying you wouldn't have to fight for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.70,0:06:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我願意幫你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but I'd be willing to give you the ammunition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.06,0:06:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:07:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我關於韋伯和巴克沃特的檔案\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My files on Webb and Buchwalter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自己看看吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why don't you take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們過幾天再談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We'll speak in a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.29,0:07:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個關於你的資料夾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, and, uh, there's one on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許你會想先讀那個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You might want to begin by reading that one first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.03,0:07:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡寧怎麼說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What'd Janine say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.17,0:07:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脫衣舞俱樂部還沒開\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Strip club's not open yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去查科佩尼科的事嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You'll look into Kapeniak?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.07,0:07:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他出現  我就能找到他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If he's on the grid, I'll find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-送我去地鐵中心站  -不去辦公室嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Drop me at metro center. - Not the office?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.45,0:07:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去找瑞秋\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna talk to Rachel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她會像昨晚那樣否認一切的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She'll deny everything, like she did last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.12,0:07:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不能否認上了斯坦普的車  你看到她了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She can't deny getting into Stamper's car. You saw her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.58,0:07:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許你可以拿篇報道她爸爸的稿子給她看\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Maybe you send a version of the story, about her dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:07:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒人會發表的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No one would print it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.96,0:07:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可瑞秋不知道啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Rachel doesn't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.61,0:08:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說"隨你便  賤人"\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She said, "Go to town, bitch."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會管用的  我得當面跟她談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It won't work. I have to get in her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.58,0:08:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.80,0:08:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我們都替你高興  -謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- We're thrilled for you. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.48,0:08:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想親自跟鮑勃和泰瑞說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I wanted to fill in Bob and Terry personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們快開始吧  我什麼時候出發去匹茲堡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now let's get to it. I have to leave for Pittsburgh in what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.51,0:08:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20分鐘後\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫吉姆衝刺  就要到終點了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Home stretch with Jim. Whistle-stop tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在形勢很好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Looking good out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確  但我們還是不想冒險\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Very good. But we don't want to take any chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接替你的黨鞭人選  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now, your replacement as whip, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.32,0:08:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鮑勃已經提出了一些想法\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Bob has already shared some thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.03,0:08:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡霍華德·韋伯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I like Howard Webb.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,韋伯不錯  你考慮過韋斯·巴克沃特嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Webb is a solid choice. Have you thought about Wes Buchwalter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴克沃特太衝動\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Buchwalter's a hot-head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.44,0:08:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼韋伯你覺得可以嗎  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, could you live with Webb, Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.51,0:08:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,韋伯懂戰術  但做事虎頭蛇尾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Webb is a good tactician, but he lacks follow-through.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.11,0:08:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴克沃特是個粗人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The problem with Buchwalter is he's too abrasive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.51,0:08:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毫無魅力  樹敵太多\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No charm. Lots of enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.33,0:08:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有別的選擇嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is there a third option?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.30,0:08:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們是黨團資歷最深的兩位  輪到他們了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They're the two most senior members in the caucus. It's their turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.60,0:08:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統先生  可不可以讓黨內成員一起挑選\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. President, what if we let the caucus pick?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家公平競爭  他們兩人都很有資質\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let it be a wide-open race. Both men are qualified.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.58,0:08:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,領導層在這事上要意見一致\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The leadership should be united in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.39,0:08:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能各自支援不同的候選人  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We don't want to be backing different candidates, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.21,0:08:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就乾脆別插手  誰都別支援誰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So we stay out of it and neither of us backs anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.49,0:08:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這挺好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.17,0:09:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黨團會尊重憑實力競爭上來的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Caucus will respect someone who did it the old-fashioned way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.34,0:09:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幾位  這事你們做主\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, gentlemen, it's your call to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們自己討論決定  然後告訴我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Figure it out amongst yourselves. Let me know what you decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.87,0:09:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.84,0:09:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫我接劉易斯部長\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Put me through to Secretary Lewis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.47,0:09:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭克  我不想為這事跟你爭\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Frank, I don't want to go to battle with you on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.80,0:09:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們犯過這種錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We've been down that road.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.86,0:09:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得是啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I couldn't agree more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公平競爭讓我緊張\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}An open race makes me nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是提議一下\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, look, it was just a suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.30,0:09:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我再想想吧  -謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- I'll put some thought into it. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.07,0:09:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去做做他的工作吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You know, let me -- let me go work on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你好運了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.63,0:09:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你來幹什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問我要點什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ask me what I want to order.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.95,0:09:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想好點什麼了嗎  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Have you decided, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.97,0:09:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你馬上辭職  告訴里昂你不幹了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I need you to quit your job. Tell Leon it's your last day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.44,0:09:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:09:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表現自然點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Act normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.85,0:10:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要什麼配菜\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did you want a side with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們能找到你一次\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They found you once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能冒險再有第二次\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We can't take the chance they'll find you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.90,0:10:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去哪弄錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What am I supposed to do about money?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.61,0:10:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照我說的做  回家  收拾東西\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do as I say. Go home and pack your things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我十點過來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll come by around ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-那我就無權決定...  -夠了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Well -- but I don't get a say in any... - Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只收拾一個箱子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}One suitcase. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.94,0:10:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你至少也告訴我...  -我要肉餡土豆餡餅\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Can you at least tell me... - I'll take the shepherd's pie
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.74,0:10:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,配菜要球芽甘藍\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}with a side of Brussels sprouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帶走\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}To go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不想上法庭  她的律師不想上法庭\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We don't want a trial. Her lawyers don't want a trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.37,0:10:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但科爾女士就是不聽勸\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But Ms. Cole won't listen to reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.56,0:10:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此  如果你再給我點時間\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That said, if you give me a little more time, I think that --
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.85,0:10:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果她想上法庭  那就隨她\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If she wants to go to court, then let's give her that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然她現在不肯講理  不代表將來...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just because she's being unreasonable now doesn't mean she --
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.68,0:10:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我受夠了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這是膝跳反應\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's a knee-jerk reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.11,0:10:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你不是個不理智不耐心的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've never known you to be a person who was irrational or impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.26,0:10:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再去找找她的律師  或許我們...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let me check back with her lawyers, and maybe we can --
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最早什麼時候能開庭\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What's the soonest we can get a trial date?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.55,0:10:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊爾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Claire...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.11,0:10:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我個大致時間\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Give me a timeframe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.85,0:10:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最早也六個月後吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Six months, at the earliest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:11:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轉告她那邊  然後就中止溝通\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Inform her people, then no more communication.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.07,0:11:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為你的律師  我有責任強烈建議你不要這麼做\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}As your counsel, it is my duty to strongly advise you against this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白  謝謝你  奧利弗\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I understand and I thank you, Oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.49,0:11:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.14,0:11:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-怎麼樣  -他們不肯透露私人聯絡方式\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- So? - They wouldn't give me individual contact info,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這裡是過去三年在東非工作過的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but here's every doctor who served in east Africa
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有醫生的名單\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}during the last three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\u1}健康維護組織{\u0}呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And what about the HMO?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}收取固定預付費用後  為特定地區主動參保人群提供全面醫療服務的體系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.00,0:11:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要同意書  也在袋子裡了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You need a consent form. And it's in the packet.
