Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.19,0:11:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\frz27.51\move(234.72,28.8,131.04,110.16,0,1300)}{\fn方正大黑_GBK\fs15\b0\bord0\shad0\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H2B2E2B&}大衛·阿普博姆醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有事嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找瑞秋·波斯納\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah. I'm looking for Rachel Posner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.52,0:11:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不在\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.42,0:11:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她晚些時候會來嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Uh, is she coming in later?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.87,0:11:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我認識她\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.07,0:11:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你朋友可把我害慘了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, your friend really screwed me over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.37,0:11:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她上班上到一半就跑了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She took off, middle of her shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不得不去找我的房東來幫忙\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I had to put my hostess on wait staff duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.93,0:12:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有點擔心  瑞秋有麻煩\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Look, I'm concerned. Rachel's in real trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.94,0:12:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管她的私人問題呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't care what her personal issues are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.05,0:12:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只想知道她住哪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I just need to know where she lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.31,0:12:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們不是認識嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I thought you knew her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.34,0:12:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們認識  但有日子沒見了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I do. It's just been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她給我發簡訊說她想自殘\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And she sent me a text message saying she wants to hurt herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.76,0:12:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在又不接電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And now she won't answer her phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.20,0:12:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她有精神病史\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She has a history of mental illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.12,0:12:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得幫幫我啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You've gotta help me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.13,0:12:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我幫不了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Look, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的工資和稅務報表  上面的地址是個郵箱\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Her W-2, the address is a P.O. Box.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.26,0:12:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼都行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll take whatever I can get.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我去辦公室幫你看看  -謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Let me see what I got in the office. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.16,0:12:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你找到她  叫她別回來了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you find her, you tell her not to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.63,0:12:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不需要瘋子來我這兒搗亂\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't need some nutcase creating chaos in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-南茜  -是  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Nancy? - Yes, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.47,0:12:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道格回來了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is Doug back yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在辦公室  還有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}In his office. And, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.37,0:12:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們開始收到生日賀卡了  還有幾件禮物\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Birthday cards have started to arrive. A few presents.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.95,0:12:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寫感謝信  記錄禮物  貴重的...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you notes. Inventory the presents. Anything valuable...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.22,0:12:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擺進會議室\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Goes in the conference room?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,便宜的...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Anything cheap...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.86,0:12:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給實習生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Goes to the interns.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:12:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道怎麼處理賀卡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And you know what to do with the cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.99,0:13:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.12,0:13:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今晚去接她\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm picking her up tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在喬帕都安排好了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I got everything set up for her in Joppa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是哪裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Where's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.61,0:13:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬里蘭  巴爾的摩北30分鐘路程\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Maryland. About 30 minutes north of Baltimore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.17,0:13:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太近了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's close to home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們想讓她消失  但我們得能找到她\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We want her to disappear, but not on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.33,0:13:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好吧  一次性電話買好了嗎  -嗯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Fine. Do you have the burner? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生日快樂\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.38,0:13:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,預付款的  你只要開機撥號就行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's prepaid. All you need to do is turn it on and dial.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.41,0:13:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電話記錄還得處理掉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We still have the phone history.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.95,0:13:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以日後更要小心了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All the more reason to be safe going forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯蒂娜怎麼樣了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Where are we with Christina?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在辦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安排她去琳達手下  我今早打過電話了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Linda's office. I called her this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是吉莉安·科爾嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are you Gillian Cole?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我們認識嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Uh, have we met?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.38,0:13:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  但你認識我丈夫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, we haven't met. You know my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.47,0:13:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你丈夫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Your husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.48,0:14:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大衛·阿普博姆\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}David Applebaum.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來是真的嘍\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.35,0:14:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那隻是個錯誤\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想看看我們的孩子嗎  我可以給你看看照片\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You want to see our kids? I can show you pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿普博姆太太  我...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mrs. Applebaum, I -- I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.67,0:14:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以為你是誰啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Who the fuck do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.93,0:14:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Look, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.17,0:14:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你抱歉  我覺得你並不抱歉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're sorry? I don't think you're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.35,0:14:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且你也休想\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And don't think for a second
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,憑這個孩子來向我們要錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}you're gonna use that baby to get money out of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他根本不知道我懷孕了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He doesn't even know I'm pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你知道他是有婦之夫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But you knew he was married.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.08,0:14:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼能這樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他說起過我們嗎  -沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Did he talk about us? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說謊的婊子  我讓你難堪了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Lying bitch. Am I embarrassing you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.42,0:14:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想過這對我和我孩子的羞辱嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did you think about how you would humiliate me and my kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.16,0:14:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再跟別人老公上床記得戴套\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Use a condom the next time you fuck somebody's husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.48,0:15:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不到24小時\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's been less than 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.26,0:15:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她正在上班就突然辭職了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She quits her job in the middle of a shift?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.21,0:15:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她害怕了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She's scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.10,0:15:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換了我也會跑\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'd take off, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.43,0:15:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是安德伍德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.71,0:15:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他行動比我們快\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's moving faster than we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.66,0:15:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脫衣舞女呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What about the stripper?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不肯開口\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Refuses to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.69,0:15:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科佩尼科呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Kapeniak?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住址不詳  沒兄弟姐妹  父母雙亡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No current address. No siblings. Parents are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑞秋是唯一的機會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Rachel's the last loose end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.49,0:15:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了酒駕  她肯定還知道點別的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She must know something else. Bigger than the DUI.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道她去哪了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Any idea where she went?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有個杜邦的郵箱地址  但管理員都沒見過她\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I got a P.O. Box in Dupont, but none of the clerks have seen her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以去那裡守株待兔\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I could go stake it out, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.35,0:15:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你找過你的人了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Have you talked to your guy yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明後天吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}In the next day or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他會把羅素自殺的警方報告拿給我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's bringing me the police report on Russo's suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我儘量多套些資訊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll press him for more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你下一步怎麼辦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And what's your next move?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想想怎麼回覆這個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Trying to figure out how to respond to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(150,0)\fs13\fn方正準圓_GBK\c&H34332B&\bord0\shad0\pos(175.2,137.7)\frz15.22}週一下午三點  地點你定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.83,0:15:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幾個小時前收到的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I got it a couple hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.15,0:15:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是在給你下套\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I think he's setting her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道怎麼應付他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know how to handle him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他知道的越少越好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The less he learns, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.61,0:15:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也許能打探到訊息\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We might learn something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.79,0:15:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是他說了算  怎麼打探\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not with him calling the shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.96,0:15:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地點是我定\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm choosing the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:15:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼區別\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}As if that makes a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.25,0:15:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又不會跟他上床  就是談話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm not gonna fuck him. Just talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.53,0:16:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去下洗手間\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna go to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.85,0:16:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-抱歉  我不該  -沒關係\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- I'm sorry. I shouldn't have -- - That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.37,0:16:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有關係\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.36,0:16:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望你疏忽大意\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I just don't want you to be careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.42,0:16:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I won't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.02,0:16:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不想有自己的生活\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You want no life?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想一個人做三個人的工作嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You want more work than three people can handle?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想找個第一個月\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You want a decent chance
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可能被炒的工作嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that you could be fired within the first month?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你感興趣  咱就接著談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If that tempts you, we can keep talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些都不是問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}None of that intimidates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.34,0:16:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過去九周裡我都在管理一個選區\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've been running a congressional district for the past nine weeks
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且沒人幫我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}with zero assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒人選舉我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Nobody elected me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.25,0:16:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒人教我怎麼做\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Nobody taught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我那麼做是因為總得有人來做\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've done it because somebody had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.65,0:16:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅素的事是個悲劇\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What happened was tragic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.36,0:16:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可我不會同情你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But you won't get sympathy from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.58,0:16:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有時間\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't have time for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.48,0:16:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要是想博取同情  也不會到這兒來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I wouldn't be sitting here if I wanted a shoulder to cry on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑞秋\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Rachel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.21,0:17:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走開\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說走開\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I said leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收拾好了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are you packed?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.59,0:17:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我哪也不去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.96,0:17:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今天沒辭職\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So you didn't quit today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.19,0:17:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辭了  可我改主意了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I did, but I changed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.19,0:17:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這事由不得你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This isn't your decision to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.11,0:17:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要回去工作  繼續住這兒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm keeping my job and I'm keeping this apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.65,0:17:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.99,0:17:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你答應過  會讓這些都過去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You promised you'd make all of this go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.59,0:17:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你得重新開始\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And you starting over is the first --
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經重新開始了  不想再來一次了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, I already started over. I don't want to start over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想你這樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I wish you didn't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.27,0:17:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾出去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.28,0:18:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾出去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.15,0:18:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小點聲\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Lower your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.55,0:18:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我殺了你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll fucking kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,動手吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.58,0:18:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我能保護你  你還不明白嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I am the only one who can protect you. Don't you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道自己現在多危險\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You have no idea how much danger you're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.48,0:18:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收拾東西吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Start packing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.65,0:18:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我每年都得問一句\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You know I ask every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.37,0:18:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過生日  像往年一樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Nothing, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.12,0:19:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以吃頓晚餐\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I thought we could have dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.32,0:19:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非是去個沒人會認出我們的地方\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Only if it's someplace where nobody will recognize us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.39,0:19:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想誰走過來...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't want anyone walking up --
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是說在家  我可以做點菜\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I mean at home. I'll cook something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要蛋糕\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.39,0:19:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不買蛋糕\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.98,0:19:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要禮物\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.82,0:19:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不買禮物\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.49,0:19:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那行  訴訟怎麼樣了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can do that. How's the lawsuit coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.08,0:19:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不會有事的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.21,0:19:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們打算將您的安保規模\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We'd like to increase the size of your detail
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.07,0:19:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,增至國家元首級別  從明天開始\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to full head of state status, starting tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可不行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, that won't be happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.30,0:19:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提前準備總是沒錯的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's good to get a head start,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.38,0:19:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣等他們宣佈...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}so that by the time they announce --
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.53,0:19:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我徹底失去隱私之前就剩這幾天了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}These are my last few days before I never have privacy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要儘量好好享受這幾天\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I intend to savor these moments for as long as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.08,0:19:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是先生  出於安全考慮  我認為...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But, sir, in terms of safety, I think --
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.64,0:19:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在國會表決認可我為副總統之前\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Until I'm confirmed as the Vice President,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.64,0:19:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}副總統一職空缺後  由總統提名  國會兩院多數票決認可  才算生效
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.37,0:19:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安保問題仍是我來決定  對嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}security is at my discretion. Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,理論上是的  但是...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Technically, yes. But --
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不就得了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then that's settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.80,0:19:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧  我們等正式宣佈\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All right. We'll wait until the announcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.07,0:19:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  經國會認可後\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now, assuming the confirmation goes through,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就要解決您搬入\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we'll need to work out the logistics
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.26,0:19:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海軍天文臺的後勤工作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}of moving you into the Naval Observatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.26,0:19:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}天文臺地界內的"天文臺一號圈"為美國副總統官邸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.52,0:19:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也不行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That won't be happening, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.11,0:19:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,議員會繼續住在他的別墅裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The congressman will be remaining in his townhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.64,0:19:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那裡沒有必要的安保基建\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But it doesn't have the necessary security infrastructure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.51,0:20:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你們就去建啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then you'll need to build it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要建防爆設施\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're talking blast-proofing,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.02,0:20:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,固定線路通訊網路  24小時辦公室空間\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}hardwired communications networks, 24-hour office space --
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.96,0:20:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有志者事竟成\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Where there's a will, there's a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會直接跟你聯絡  討論改建計劃\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll contact you directly about setting a plan in motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.62,0:20:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你走之前  還有件事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And one last thing before you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.25,0:20:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把艾德華·密查姆安排在我的安保隊伍裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'd like to have Edward Meechum serve on my detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.40,0:20:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是國會警察\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's Capitol Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.59,0:20:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前是  你要調他去特勤處\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}For now. You're about to appoint him to the Secret Service.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那得經過加速培訓\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That would require an accelerated training program.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.18,0:20:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生  我們有很多合格的特工\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sir, we have plenty of qualified agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.11,0:20:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有男有女  都有豐富經驗\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Men and women with years of experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.74,0:20:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很期待與他們合作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I look forward to working with all of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.28,0:20:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要艾德華·密查姆也是安保隊一員就行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}as long as Edward Meechum is on the detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你前來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you very much for your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.57,0:20:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you, sir.
