Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.53,0:20:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs12\fad(0,800)\fn方正準圓_GBK\c&HFFFFFF&\bord0\b1\shad0\pos(246.24,206.64)\clip(235,204,241,222)\t(0,818,\clip(235,205,258,222)}我就來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.94,0:20:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,南茜  讓密查姆把車開過來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Nancy, have Meechum bring the car around.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.13,0:21:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上一次就是最後一次\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You know, the last time was the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.94,0:21:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  但這很重要\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know. But this is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.40,0:21:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你總想拉我下水  我不幹了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You keep selling me that swampland. I'm done buying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.66,0:21:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再也不幹了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.57,0:21:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掩蓋酒駕的事  你說能牽扯到巴尼·豪爾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Cover-up. You said it went as high as Barney Hull.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.06,0:21:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是那麼說的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's not what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.03,0:21:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把瑞秋·波斯納的拘捕記錄給我時...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When you gave me Rachel Posner's arrest file --
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.32,0:21:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說的是  肯定有大人物干預  記錄才會消失\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What I said is that arrests don't disappear without a big-ass wand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.18,0:21:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那可不能當做證據\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That ain't the same as proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們認為這事牽扯到議會領導層\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We think the congressional leadership took part.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.46,0:21:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不關心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.29,0:21:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  你關心  我知道你關心的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, you do. I know you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.47,0:21:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我真的不關心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, I really don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.90,0:21:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當年你幫我暴露毒品...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When you helped me expose the drug --
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.14,0:21:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們不過是拿點小恩小惠的街頭黑警\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They were dirty street cops stuffing a few grams in their pockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.75,0:21:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這事可不一樣  都是有權有勢的大人物\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is different. Powerful fucking people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.30,0:21:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑警就是黑警  你想保護他們嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Dirty cops are dirty cops. You want to protect them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.37,0:21:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還有養老保險和家人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have a pension and a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.58,0:21:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白  但是...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I understand. But --
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再聯繫我了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't contact me again.
