Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.10,0:22:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的手機在哪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Where's your cell?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.25,0:22:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡  我沒在錄音\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Here. It's not recording.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.07,0:22:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得刪掉我們之間所有的通話記錄\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I need to ask you to delete all of our phone history.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.07,0:22:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我為什麼要刪掉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why would I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這是在保護我們兩個人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm trying to protect both you and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.97,0:22:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要坐牢的又不是我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm not facing prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.23,0:22:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他酒駕不是你替他掩蓋的嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You didn't cover up the arrest?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.62,0:22:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是因為你想讓他競選州長\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is it because you wanted him to be governor?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.97,0:23:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是  他惹了麻煩  我就伸了援手\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. He was in trouble, so I helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.66,0:23:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後他表現出參選意願  我就提供了指導\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And later he expressed a desire to run, and I offered guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.69,0:23:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指導一個酒鬼嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}To an alcoholic?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.00,0:23:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他當時戒了酒  正在恢復中\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}To a sober recovering alcoholic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.62,0:23:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是指望他會自毀前程嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did you want him to self-sabotage?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.10,0:23:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然不是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.66,0:23:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他沒戲了  馬修斯才來參選\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It got Matthews in the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.25,0:23:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我願意支援有上進心的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I like to back people who want to succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.15,0:23:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如說你自己\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Take yourself as an example.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.97,0:23:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不過是漁翁得利\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You just took advantage of the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.93,0:23:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得利的是馬修斯  我沒指望能當副總統啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Matthews took advantage. I didn't seek the nomination.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.67,0:23:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅素死的時候坐在副駕座上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Russo was in the passenger seat when he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.73,0:23:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這話不準確\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's not entirely accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.17,0:23:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看過警方報告\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I saw the police report.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.73,0:23:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還直接和警局局長談過呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I spoke to the commissioner directly,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.65,0:23:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我關心彼得  我想瞭解全部細節\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}because I cared about Peter and I wanted to know the full story.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.86,0:23:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那他沒坐在副駕座上嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He wasn't in the passenger seat?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.59,0:23:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副駕座的車門開著  他半邊身子躺在外面\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The passenger door was open, and he was halfway out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.94,0:23:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警方認為\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They think that...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.07,0:23:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他可能中途後悔了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}he might have had second thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.48,0:23:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我去問巴尼·豪爾  他會證實你的話嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If I speak to Barney Hull, he'll confirm that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.46,0:24:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼意思  佐伊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What are you suggesting, Zoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.47,0:24:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許有人謀殺了他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Maybe there was foul play.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.71,0:24:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是有任何謀殺的跡象\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If there was a hint of foul play,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.09,0:24:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得警方會不去調查嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}don't you think the police would have investigated?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.17,0:24:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這些掩蓋他酒駕的警察嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The same police that buried his DUI?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.17,0:24:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你認為我也脫不了干係\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And you think I was involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.56,0:24:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們之間有聯繫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There's a connection between you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.23,0:24:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽聽你在說什麼  荒唐至極\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}listen to you. You sound ludicrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.07,0:24:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是問問而已\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm just asking questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.49,0:24:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  你這是在瞎猜  瞎聯繫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, you're connecting dots that don't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.82,0:24:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓我別插手  裝作什麼都不知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You want me to just walk away? Act as if I don't know anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.03,0:24:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  是我替彼得解了圍\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, I got Peter out of a jam.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.26,0:24:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  我讓他去找科佩尼科\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, I sent him to speak to Kapeniak.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.32,0:24:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但除此之外  就沒別的了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But beyond that, there's nothing to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.34,0:24:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別怪我  但現在我實在沒法相信你的話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can you blame me if I find it difficult to trust you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.01,0:24:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,信不信隨你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Trust me or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.54,0:24:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很快就要獲得認可正式成為副總統了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but I'm about to be confirmed as the vice president.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.29,0:24:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的合作關係已經延伸到總統層面了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And our relationship extends to the Oval Office now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.85,0:24:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別無緣無故地沒事找事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't step out of the sunlight for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.05,0:24:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們忘記過去  展開新的合作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's start this new chapter with a clean slate.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.57,0:24:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回去好好想想  我會聯繫你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now you sleep on that, and I'll be in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.15,0:25:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們先做血液和激素檢測\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We'll start with blood and hormone tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.35,0:25:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果幾天之內就能出來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Those results should be back within a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.35,0:25:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果結果不錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If they're good,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.94,0:25:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就開始對你和你丈夫進行基因檢測\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we'll move on to genetic testing for both you and your husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.20,0:25:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和他談過了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Have you spoken to him yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.78,0:25:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有  我想先做檢測\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not yet. I want to do the tests first.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.02,0:25:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這周什麼時間做都可以\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We can do those anytime this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.92,0:25:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會讓我的人跟你這邊聯絡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll have my office call yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.45,0:25:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差點忘了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I almost forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.25,0:25:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我上網做了些研究\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've been doing some research on the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.37,0:25:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,網上的話不能都信啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Be careful of the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.12,0:25:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在搜索四十歲以上孕婦的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I was looking into common issues
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.28,0:25:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孕期常見問題時\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}associated with post-40 pregnancies,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.30,0:25:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,查到了一個藥物\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and this drug came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.22,0:25:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但沒查到什麼詳細資訊  它叫靜脈\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But there wasn't much on it. It's Cruvenae...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.52,0:25:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靜脈雌酮\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Cruvenae-tenuestrin.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.58,0:25:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒找到詳細資訊是因為這種藥\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You probably haven't found much because it's,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.31,0:25:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還處在測試階段\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}still in the beta stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.02,0:25:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這藥物有什麼療效\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And what does it do?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.67,0:25:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它能促進血液流往胎盤\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It helps maximize blood flow to the placenta.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.61,0:25:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此前還沒有哪種藥物能做到這一點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Until CVT there hasn't been any viable drug for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.94,0:25:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這藥目前仍有爭議\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The jury's still out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.41,0:25:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是各年齡段的女性都可能患上胎盤機能不全\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But placental insufficiency affects women of all ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.10,0:25:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在先別擔心這個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I wouldn't worry about it for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.30,0:25:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們還是按部就班  慢慢來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's putting the cart way before the horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.70,0:26:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬修斯已經穩操勝券\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You know, Matthews has this locked up,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.52,0:26:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是國會保守人士認為\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but conservatives on the hill are saying
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.99,0:26:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他這次重回州長之位  還會像從前一樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}he's gonna return to Harrisburg with the same myopic,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.84,0:26:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目光短淺  增加赤字\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}deficit-growing mentality.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.31,0:26:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至於馬修斯獲勝後接任副總統的人選\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now, as to who's gonna replace Matthews when he wins...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.92,0:26:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把牆燈關上不礙事吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can I at least turn off the overhead?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.13,0:26:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然沒事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.99,0:26:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...還能有誰在財政上更恣意妄為...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}...someone even more fiscally irresponsible...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.72,0:26:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要我去樓下工作嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you want me to go work downstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.10,0:26:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用  沒事  給我騰個地方就行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. That's fine. Just make some room.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.53,0:26:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還沒表態呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You haven't said a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.51,0:26:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.92,0:26:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們怎麼辦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Where does that leave us?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.49,0:26:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我完全準備好了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm fully prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.03,0:26:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早就蓄勢待發了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I have been for some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.86,0:27:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你會做出你認為最好的決定\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know you'll do whatever you think is best.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.89,0:27:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是安德伍德確認了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But Underwood confirmed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.27,0:27:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他將被提名為副總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's gonna be tapped for VP.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.96,0:27:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那對我們一點幫助也沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That doesn't get us any closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.94,0:27:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們知道羅素的死給馬修斯掃清了障礙\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, we know that Russo cleared the way for Matthews.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.50,0:27:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能印證理論  但不是證據\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It reinforces the theory. It doesn't give us proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.48,0:27:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能指責他耍卑鄙手段\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We can't go after the guy for playing dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.61,0:27:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那根本不算新聞\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's not news.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.40,0:27:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國會裡一半的混蛋都在耍手段\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Half the fuckers in Congress play dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.09,0:27:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他扶持一個假候選人  就為到時搞垮他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He propped up a sham candidate, just to take him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.19,0:27:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上沒人強迫羅素喝酒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Nobody forced Russo to drink that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.64,0:27:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙本來就是個酒鬼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The guy was an alcoholic.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.72,0:27:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  除了三天後他自殺了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Okay, we don't know what happened that night,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.05,0:27:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於那晚我們一無所知\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}other than three days later he killed himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.15,0:27:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還會再聯繫他嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are you gonna contact him again?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.76,0:27:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.64,0:27:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們得放慢進度  退一步重新考慮\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We need to slow down, take a step back, and reevaluate.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.77,0:27:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經讓瑞秋溜走了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We already let Rachel slip away.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.38,0:27:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非掌握更多資訊  否則都是徒勞\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There's no point until we have more.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.87,0:27:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們應該讓他去猜  而不是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We should keep him guessing, not --
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.59,0:27:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等  從哪裡打探更多資訊  從誰那裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Wait-- have more from where? From who?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.51,0:27:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.92,0:27:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我們應該先嘗試別的辦法\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But we should exhaust all options
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.27,0:27:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-再考慮讓佐伊去聯繫安德伍德  -但我們別無選擇\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- before Zoe reaches back out to Underwood. - But we don't have any options.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.05,0:27:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-那會顯得我們別無選擇  -我們已經撞南牆了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- It looks desperate. - We are up against a brick wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.76,0:27:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非安德伍德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And unless Underwood--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.51,0:27:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐伊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Zoe...?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.25,0:28:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要一個人想想\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I just need to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.80,0:28:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起討論吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, let's think about it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.24,0:28:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天給你打電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll call you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.43,0:28:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗萊迪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Freddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.53,0:28:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah, Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.68,0:28:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今早的肋排是不是有什麼不同\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Was there something different about these ribs this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.47,0:28:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更好吃了還是難吃了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Better or worse?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.18,0:28:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本以為你的肋排是美味到極致了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I didn't think that they could get any better,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.96,0:28:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過今天的真是不同凡響\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but these were something special.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.17,0:28:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換了一個新屠夫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, tried a new butcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.77,0:28:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他慢慢地給豬放血\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Slow-bleeds his hogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.46,0:28:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這屠宰方法不合法  但是...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It ain't legal, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.91,0:28:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會告訴別人的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I won't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.67,0:28:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道還會不會再去他那裡買肉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't know if I'm gonna go back to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.32,0:28:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去他的店\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Went out to his shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.82,0:28:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店後有個房間\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's got a room in the back
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.22,0:28:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就在那裡殺豬\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}where he does it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.31,0:28:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,房間是隔音的  裡面裝備齊全\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Soundproof. A whole setup.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.47,0:28:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要弄成隔音的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}W-- why soundproof?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.97,0:28:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為豬叫得太厲害\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}'Cause of how they scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.98,0:28:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它們能嗅到死神來臨的氣息\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They can smell it coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.32,0:28:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,往它們的喉嚨裡插根管子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You stick that pipe in their throat,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.91,0:28:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來的十分鐘簡直生不如死\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the next 10 minutes is hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.80,0:28:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的鼓膜都能被震破\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Bust your fucking eardrums.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.21,0:28:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人性化的方式是速戰速決\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now, the humane way to do it is to make it quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.46,0:29:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裝作餵食那樣提一桶泔水來  然後  砰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Bring out a bucket of slop like it's feeding time and -- -- bam.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.37,0:29:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對準後腦勺來上一鍬\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Shovel right to the base of the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.72,0:29:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,豬一聲也不會吭\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No screaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.93,0:29:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博奇同意公開競爭  但他說的很清楚\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's willing to open up the race, but Birch was very clear:
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.54,0:29:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他不能支援誰  你也不行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}if he can't endorse anyone, you can't either.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.38,0:29:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很公平\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.94,0:29:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的希望巴克沃特勝選\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You really want Buchwalter to win?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.50,0:29:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望最優秀的人能勝選\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want the best man to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.66,0:29:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謹小慎微的廢話  說了等於沒說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That sounds like a cagey bullshit non-answer to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.14,0:29:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想插手這件事  泰瑞\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm on the sidelines for this one, Terry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.54,0:29:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事你不插手  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're never on the sidelines, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.70,0:29:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回頭見\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll see you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.90,0:29:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs9\fad(0,800)\fn方正準圓_GBK\c&HFFFFFF&\bord0\shad0\pos(261.12,192.24)}未知號碼
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.90,0:29:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs12\fad(0,800)\fn方正準圓_GBK\c&HFFFFFF&\bord0\b1\shad0\pos(282.24,203.32)}我們能重新開始了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.54,0:29:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊爾  你不回我電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Claire. You wouldn't return my calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.57,0:29:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就回來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.18,0:30:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的律師說我不應該再和你接觸\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My attorney said that I shouldn't be in contact with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.08,0:30:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\u1}藍十字會{\u0}告訴我保險被取消了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Blue Cross said my insurance was canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.08,0:30:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}為會員及其家屬提供住院等醫療保險的非贏利組織
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.53,0:30:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解僱金條款裡規定了一年的健康保險\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The severance package gave me health coverage for up to a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.00,0:30:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That sounds right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.74,0:30:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以肯定出了什麼問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So there must be some kind of mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.51,0:30:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得去跟保險公司說啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, you'll have to talk to the insurance company.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.04,0:30:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去了  他們說保險被終止了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I did. They said it was terminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.48,0:30:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果僱主不同意  他們就無法恢復\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They can't reinstate it without the employer's approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.75,0:30:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓我幫你一把\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And you want me to get involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.97,0:30:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一些我需要的藥物\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There's medication that I need
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.18,0:30:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須通過健康維護組織獲取\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that I can't get unless it goes through my HMO.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.08,0:30:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這我知道  我看過你的檔案\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm well aware. I-- I reviewed your records.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.23,0:30:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-什麼  -你簽了同意書\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- What? - You signed a consent form.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.51,0:30:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. I-- I-- I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.03,0:30:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你偽造了我的簽名嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You forged my signature?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.24,0:30:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿普博姆太太是不是去找過你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did a Mrs. Applebaum pay you a visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.66,0:30:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道你這麼做是...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You realize what you're doing is--
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.28,0:31:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,民事罪  不是刑事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Civil. Not criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.35,0:31:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想清楚了嗎  因為等我們上了法庭\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Have you thought this out? Because when we go to court--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.39,0:31:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六個月後嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You mean six months from now?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.86,0:31:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還有四個月就生了  不是嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're expecting in four, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.48,0:31:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你這四個月就沒有藥物可用\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's four months without the medicine you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.82,0:31:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有必要的話  我寧願讓你的孩子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm wiling to let your child wither and die inside you
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.79,0:31:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夭折在你肚子裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}if that's what's required.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.60,0:31:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我們都不想看到那種結果\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But neither of us wants that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.16,0:31:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說說看  你真想和我做敵人嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now tell me, am I really the sort of enemy you want to make?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.08,0:31:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你還有選擇\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But here's the alternative.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.77,0:31:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這家機構  這些員工\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This office, this staff,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.81,0:31:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一年兩千兩百萬美元都給你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}22 million a year could be yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.66,0:31:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,淨水計劃也是你的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The CWI could be yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.75,0:31:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你我的恩怨一筆勾銷\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And you and me, we wash our hands of each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.38,0:31:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想收買我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're trying to buy me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.39,0:31:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我們初見時我答應給你權力\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. When we first met, I promised to empower you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.72,0:31:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這是在兌現諾言\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm fulfilling that promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.06,0:31:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你騙我怎麼辦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How do I get screwed?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.01,0:31:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會的  我辭職  你取代我的職位\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You don't. I resign. You take my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.76,0:31:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒其他條件嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No strings?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.63,0:31:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}None.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.15,0:31:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,民調顯示吉姆·馬修斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Exit polls have Jim Matthews winning
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.73,0:31:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將以9到12個百分點的絕對優勢贏得競選\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}by anywhere from a nine-to-twelve-percent margin of victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.86,0:32:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.77,0:32:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安德伍德太太嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mrs. Underwood?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.02,0:32:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.72,0:32:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好  這裡是拉森醫生辦公室\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hi. I'm calling from Dr. Larson's office
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.03,0:32:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟您確認一下明早十點的血檢和尿檢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to confirm your 10 a.m. tomorrow for the blood and urine tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.83,0:32:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去不了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.75,0:32:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果明天不行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, if tomorrow doesn't work,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.27,0:32:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以重新安排到週四  甚至週一\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we can reschedule for Thursday or even Monday--
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.91,0:32:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  別給我安排了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, I won't be rescheduling.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.29,0:32:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請替我感謝拉森醫生的會診\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Please tell Dr. Larson I appreciate all her consultation,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.47,0:32:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我經過再三考慮\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but I've put a great deal of thought into this
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.55,0:32:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決定不再進行其他檢測了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and I won't be pursuing any further tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.38,0:32:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.60,0:32:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}(無訊號)
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.06,0:34:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你考慮過我們之前討論的事了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Have you thought about what we discussed?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.78,0:34:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說得沒錯  我們是該拋開過去  重新開始\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I think you're right. We should start with a clean slate.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.47,0:34:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的簡訊呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What about our text messages?
