Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.98,0:34:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們之間沒事吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are we good?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.47,0:34:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.34,0:34:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們忘記這些亂七八糟的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And we can put all this other nonsense behind us
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.61,0:34:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,互相信任  互相幫助  可以嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and trust one another and continue to help one another?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.86,0:34:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣很好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'd like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.41,0:34:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那現在算是拋開過去了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then consider the slate clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.72,0:34:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回答我個問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Answer me one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.75,0:34:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副駕座的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The passenger seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.40,0:34:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說羅素是想出去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You said Russo was trying to get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.12,0:34:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這沒什麼奇...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That there was nothing ab--
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.16,0:34:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是剛剛說好...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I thought we just agreed to--
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.31,0:34:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想相信你  但你得說明白\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want to believe you, but I need details.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.86,0:34:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有所隱瞞\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}More than what you're sharing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.86,0:34:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想問什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What's your question?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.08,0:35:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅素酒癮復發當晚  他出席了一個募捐活動\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The night Russo fell off the wagon he was at a fundraiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.44,0:35:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麥克奈利癌症研究所...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The McNeally Cancer Institute--
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.77,0:35:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警察報告裡全都有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All in the police report.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.20,0:35:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑞秋·波斯納當晚也在那家酒店\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Rachel Posner was at the hotel that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.44,0:35:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.17,0:35:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅素被捕時跟他在一起的應召女\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The call girl who was with Russo when he was arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.54,0:35:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又不知道她叫什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I didn't know her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.94,0:35:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她消失了  弗蘭西斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She disappeared, Francis.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.90,0:35:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.87,0:35:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別裝不知道  我給行李員看了張照片\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't act surprised. I showed the bellmen a photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.42,0:35:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其中一個記得見過她\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}One of them remembers seeing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.53,0:35:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是個妓女\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The girl's a prostitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.93,0:35:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她肯定經常出現在各種酒店\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm sure she frequents many hotels.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.18,0:35:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可偏巧那晚去那家酒店嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But that hotel on that night?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.40,0:35:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這語氣像斯克斯基女士似的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, now you sound like Ms. Skorsky talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.27,0:35:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒和任何人說過這事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I haven't discussed this with anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.51,0:35:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想先問你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I wanted to ask you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.23,0:35:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道那晚發生了什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have no idea what happened that night,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.36,0:35:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只知道彼得又開始酗酒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}except that Peter started drinking again.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.46,0:35:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道有誰在場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't know who was or wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.48,0:35:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真希望我在\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I wish I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.01,0:35:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定我能阻止他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Maybe I could have stopped him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.88,0:35:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道瑞秋在哪嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you know where Rachel is?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.80,0:35:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信我的話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Listen to what I am saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.21,0:35:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是想要保護我們兩個人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I am trying to protect us both.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.14,0:35:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰都有可能問這些問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}These are questions anyone could ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.84,0:36:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但現在只有你在問\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But no one is, except you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.53,0:36:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真不知你想幹什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't imagine what you're after.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.10,0:36:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我冒了個險\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I took a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.17,0:36:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跑去你家  任你擺佈\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Showed up at your house and placed myself at your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.95,0:36:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於公於私都跨過了道德底線\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Crossed ethical lines, professionally, physically.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.25,0:36:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我願意為這些事負責\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I hold myself accountable for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.85,0:36:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這都是我的選擇  我願承擔後果\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Those were my choices, and I can live with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.92,0:36:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也希望向前看\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'd like to move forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.14,0:36:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我需要知道我到底捲入了什麼事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but I need to know exactly what I was a part of. That...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.12,0:36:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要確定我沒有捲入...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that I wasn't a part of someone's...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.44,0:36:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把話說完\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Finish your thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.89,0:36:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起謀殺\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Part of someone's murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.41,0:36:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天哪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.77,0:36:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要相信你  弗蘭西斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want to believe you, Francis.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.68,0:36:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know you --
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.59,0:39:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡寧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Janine!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.95,0:39:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快進來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.76,0:39:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打不通你電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've been calling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.07,0:39:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進屋坐吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Come in. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.12,0:39:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝點什麼嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Um, you -- you want something?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.88,0:39:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水  或者果汁\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Some, uh, water or, um, juice?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.66,0:39:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要出門\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You going somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.65,0:40:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hey. You going somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.40,0:40:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去我媽媽那裡  在伊薩卡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}To my mom's. In Ithaca.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.38,0:40:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-什麼  -我要走了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- What? - I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.65,0:40:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不不  不行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. No, no, no. No. No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.21,0:40:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我們什麼都沒有  -你要放棄嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- We have nothing. - Are you giving up on this?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.45,0:40:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這世上只有三個人知道他幹了什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There are only three people in the world that know what he has done,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.42,0:40:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其中一個已經死了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and one of them is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.88,0:40:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們有證據  盧卡斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If we had anything, Lucas,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.70,0:40:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任何確鑿證據\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}any hard evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.73,0:40:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕是一個願意公開的資訊源\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}or even a fucking quote from a source that would go on record for us,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.35,0:40:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也好說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that would be one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.43,0:40:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可我們純粹在捕風捉影  而他不是鬧著玩的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But we are grasping, and he is not fucking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.79,0:40:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你說服佐伊追查這事的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You were the one who told Zoe to pursue this.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.96,0:40:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她告訴了我你說的話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She told me what you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.10,0:40:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能把你嚇壞的文章才是真正重要的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The only stories that mattered were the ones that scared you to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.87,0:40:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可不僅僅是死亡威脅\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Okay, this isn't just death threats.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.36,0:40:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是來真的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is real.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.03,0:40:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不知道你  但他知道我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He doesn't know about you, but he knows about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.96,0:40:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是在我郵箱裡發現的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}These were in my mailbox.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.48,0:40:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有發信地址\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No return address.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.87,0:40:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他照了她的照片\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He took these of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.47,0:40:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還能是誰  你留著吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Who else? You can keep them.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.13,0:40:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不認為這對你有什麼幫助\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I don't think they're gonna help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.21,0:40:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須阻止他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We need to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.06,0:40:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變態混蛋\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sick fucking shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.31,0:40:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡寧  你不能就這麼逃跑\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Janine, you cannot run away from this!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.91,0:41:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這一輩子從來都找硬骨頭啃\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My entire career, I have always chosen the tough stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.87,0:41:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一向無所畏懼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have been fearless.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.13,0:41:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可你猜怎麼著\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.27,0:41:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這回真的害怕極了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm really fucking scared this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.59,0:41:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他重權在握\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's got power.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.91,0:41:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他輸不起\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's got a lot to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.23,0:41:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在他完全佔了上風\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And right now he is winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.50,0:41:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託  我需要你幫助  別這樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Please, I need your help. Please, don't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.52,0:41:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別做夢了  盧卡斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just wake the fuck up, Lucas!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.51,0:41:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事故發生於昨晚八點左右\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The incident occurred at approximately eight p.m. last night
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.22,0:41:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在大教堂高地地鐵站北向的列車軌道上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}on the northbound tracks of the Cathedral Heights metro station.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.89,0:41:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,華盛頓特區警察已經判定是一起意外\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}D.C. Police have ruled the death an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.91,0:41:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(98.4,185.04)\clip(73,185,129,200)\t(819,896,\clip(115,183,124,201)}{\fn方正大黑_GBK\fs14\b1\bord0\shad0\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H080809&}佐伊·巴恩斯
