Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.91,0:41:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(219.84,229.68)\clip(185,226,264,245)\t(1612,1987,\clip(211,225,264,245)}{\fn方正準圓_GBK\fs11\b1\bord0\shad0\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H1C1B18&}新聞界對事故表示哀悼
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.37,0:41:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐伊·巴恩斯是頭條網的資深撰稿人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Zoe Barnes was a senior contributor at slugline.com.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.16,0:41:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(98.4,185.04)\clip(69,173,76,203)\t(0,404,\clip(69,178,128,203)}{\fn方正大黑_GBK\fs14\b1\bord0\shad0\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H080809&}{\blur0\t(2641,3073,\blur4}佐伊·巴恩斯
