Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.71,0:41:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(149.76,213.84)\clip(130,212,151,226)\t(20,200,\clip(130,212,139,226)}{\fn方正大黑_GBK\fs13\b1\bord0\shad0\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H1C1B18&} 地鐵悲劇
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.17,0:41:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此前她曾在《華盛頓先驅報》\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Previously she worked at the Washington Herald
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.68,0:41:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做都市新聞記者和政治記者\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}as a metro reporter and political correspondent.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.60,0:41:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴恩斯報道過多條重要新聞\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Barnes broke several major stories,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.82,0:41:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包括教育改革法案的草案\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}include an early draft of the Education Reform and Achievement Act,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.54,0:42:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及導致邁克爾·科恩參議員\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}as well as a college newspaper article
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.62,0:42:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,未能被提名國務卿的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that derailed Senator Michael Kern's
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.06,0:42:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一篇公報社論\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}nomination for Secretary of State...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.93,0:42:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得那些檔案怎麼樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What'd you think of the files?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.86,0:42:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有不少可以下手的地方\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There's plenty to work with.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.06,0:42:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看了自己的嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did you look at your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.64,0:42:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裡面什麼都沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There was nothing there.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.13,0:42:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裡面該有什麼嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Should there be?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.97,0:42:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不應該\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.05,0:42:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即便你在撒謊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Even if you're lying,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.88,0:42:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我現在什麼也沒找到\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the fact that I haven't been able to find anything
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.46,0:42:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這說明你很擅長隱藏蹤跡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}tells me you're very good at covering your tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.09,0:42:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這點對我來說很寶貴  這裡就是我們的戰場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's, uh, valuable to me. Here's our battleground.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.08,0:42:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,113票\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}113 votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.60,0:42:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來你已經掌握大致情況了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You have the skeletons.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.54,0:42:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我失敗了  他們不會放過我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If I lose, they'll come after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.88,0:43:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是你必須承擔的風險\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's a risk you have to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.50,0:43:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼知道你不是在利用我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How do I know you're not just using me?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.90,0:43:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為別人競選製造障礙\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Throwing a wrench into someone else's bid?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.84,0:43:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是另一種風險  你也可以選擇等上十年\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's another risk. The alternative is you wait 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.75,0:43:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你選我肯定是有原因的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You chose me for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.49,0:43:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道是什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'd like to know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.26,0:43:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.23,0:43:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你發起過多少次導彈攻擊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How many missile strikes did you launch?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.47,0:43:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多到讓我整夜不能安睡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Enough to keep me awake at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.93,0:43:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你還是那麼做了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But you did it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.12,0:43:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  沒錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.10,0:43:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會傷及多少婦女兒童\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How many women and children?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.59,0:43:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太多了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Too many.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.74,0:43:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算知道會傷及無辜\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And you launched those missiles
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.81,0:43:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還是義無反顧地發射了導彈\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}knowing all those innocent people would die.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.71,0:43:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是奉命殲滅敵人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I had orders to eliminate the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.82,0:43:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而你專業高效地完成了任務\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Which you carried out expertly and efficiently.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.83,0:43:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你殺過人嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Have you ever killed anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.94,0:43:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.98,0:43:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾親眼目睹整棟大樓  整個村莊蕩然無存\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I watched apartment buildings, entire villages gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.88,0:43:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像不曾存在過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}like they were never there.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.07,0:43:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以  我不想再談這個話題了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'd prefer not to talk about it, if that's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.30,0:43:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你完成需要完成的任務\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You did what needed to be done,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.60,0:43:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我選擇你的原因  傑姬\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and that's why I chose you, Jackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.35,0:43:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,服役背景  歷史清白\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Service background. Clean history.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.29,0:44:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上相  我全都看好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Photogenic. The whole package.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.08,0:44:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但更重要的是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But more importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.27,0:44:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,堅決  務實\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}ruthless pragmatism.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.96,0:44:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們能合作嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are we working together or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.33,0:44:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有公開或私下表示支援巴克沃特的嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Any public or private endorsements for Buchwalter,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.91,0:44:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我支援韋伯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I come out for Webb.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.85,0:44:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不參與爭論  我向你保證\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll stay out of the fray. I give you my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.01,0:44:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也一樣  泰瑞\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Same goes for you, Terry.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.47,0:44:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  克里斯蒂娜\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Christina.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.62,0:44:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.37,0:44:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統先生  賓州情況怎麼樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. President. How was Pennsylvania?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.87,0:44:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡印度菜嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You like Indian?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.33,0:45:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生  我看到新聞了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sir? I've seen the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.64,0:45:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道她跟您很親近\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know she was close to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.24,0:45:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可怕的悲劇啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Terrible tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.50,0:45:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天特別探員洛克蘭來找過我  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Spoke to Special Agent Rockland today, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.43,0:45:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我下週開始培訓\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I begin my training next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.80,0:45:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.51,0:45:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道已經晚了一天\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know it's a day late.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.95,0:45:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但願這樣不失妥當\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hope it isn't inappropriate,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.11,0:45:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想給您這個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but I wanted to give you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.03,0:45:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  密查姆\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Meechum.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.90,0:46:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾德華真是太貼心了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That was very nice of Edward.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.80,0:46:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不該為我花這種錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He shouldn't have spent this sorta money on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.80,0:46:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在樓下開了酒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've opened some wine downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.47,0:46:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就下去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll be down in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.62,0:46:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我把你忘了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did you think I'd forgotten you?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.00,0:46:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許你希望我已經忘了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Perhaps you hoped I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.24,0:46:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別浪費時間哀悼巴恩斯小姐了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't waste a breath mourning Ms. Barnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.64,0:46:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每隻小貓都會長大\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Every kitten grows up to be a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.97,0:46:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一開始看起來都很無害\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They seem so harmless at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.97,0:46:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幼小  安靜  舔著淺盤裡的牛奶\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Small, quiet, lapping up their saucer of milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.60,0:46:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但爪子一旦長長了  貓就會撓人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But once their claws get long enough, they draw blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.59,0:46:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有時甚至會撓養貓人的手\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sometimes from the hand that feeds them.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.24,0:46:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對於我們這些爬向食物鏈頂端的人來說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}For those of us climbing to the top of the food chain,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.40,0:46:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決不能心慈手軟\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}there can be no mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.43,0:46:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有一條規則  不做獵人  便為獵物\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There is but one rule: hunt or be hunted.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.62,0:46:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Welcome back.
